description.p:
In a fifth aspect of the invention, there is provided a method of making a concrete composite, comprising:
a. providing aggregate;
b. providing a binder;
c. providing a thermoelectric material, wherein the thermoelectric material comprises a complex sulphide mineral;
d. mixing the aggregate, the binder and the thermoelectric material to form a mixture; and
e. forming the mixture into the composite, wherein the composite comprises at least 20 wt % concrete.

The present invention relates to a method of making a concrete composite, comprising:
a. providing aggregate;
b. providing a binder;
c. providing a thermoelectric material, wherein the thermoelectric material comprises a complex sulphide mineral;
d. mixing the aggregate, the binder and the thermoelectric material to form a mixture; and
e. forming the mixture into the composite, wherein the composite comprises at least 20 wt % concrete.

The present invention relates to a method of making a concrete composite, comprising:
A. providing aggregate;
B. providing a binder;
C. providing a block of polymer matrix, wherein a thermoelectric material is distributed in the polymer matrix, wherein the thermoelectric material comprises a complex sulphide mineral;
D. mixing the aggregate and the binder to form a mixture; and
E. positioning the block in the mixture to form the composite.
